data.description: This Captivating, impeccably Remodeled home in the highly desirable Spanish Hills Privately Gated Golf Club Villas Community is a True Masterpiece. Located in close proximity to Spanish Hills Country Club and Private Golf Course this home offers Peaceful Living at it's Finest. Key Features Include: Soaring Ceilings and an Open Inviting Layout, Oak Wood Wide Plank Flooring, This Kitchen, a True Highlight, with Custom Copper Hammered Farmstyle Sink, Quartz Countertops, beautiful Cabinetry and Center Island. Private Main Bedroom with Views from Balcony, Large Walk-in Closet, Upgraded carpets, incredible en-suite Bath, large Shower with Custom inlays, Graciously sized Secondary Bedroom set away to other side of the home, large walk in closet, upgraded Carpets, Upstairs Full Bath is simply Stunning, upstairs laundry.  This home is Impeccable.  Step outside to the Huge Patio complete with Fireplace and BBQ area perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. The Landscaping  and Ocean Breezes add to the Charm of the Outdoor space, Creating an Inviting atmosphere for all seasons.  Additional amenities include Epoxy Garage Floors, HVAC, Freshly Painted Throughout, Newly Plumbed above slab PEX, Private Association Pool, Spa, community room, RV Parking (Please confirm with HOA).Nestled between Malibu and Santa Barbara, Camarillo and this Spanish Hills Community is loaded with character and charm.  You're going to love it here!
